Package: lab5Package
Type: Package
Title: Latitude and Longitude Retrieval
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Priya Patil and Sangeeth Menon
Maintainer: Priya Patil <pripa640@student.liu.se>
Description: This package provides functions to retrieve latitude and longitude coordinates for a given location using external APIs. The main function, `lat_long()`, takes a location string as input and returns a list containing the latitude and longitude coordinates of the specified location. The package relies on services such as Nominatim from OpenStreetMap to fetch the geographic coordinates.
